fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 advanced 33.60 points or 0.18% to settle at 18,348. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, advanced 0.27% to 12.61. Adani Enterprises, Adani Ports and Special Economic Zone and Reliance Industries were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
